You can count on the Maryland Science Center to be there for you with educational content, DIY Science projects, experiments, video, and live stream activities that encourage interaction and spark curiosity. But we also are counting on you. With your help we can ensure that MSC remains vital and active as we navigate uncharted waters together—bridging the gap until we can open our doors once again, send our outreach teams back on the road to deliver programming in every county in Maryland again, and deploy our teams back out to Early Learning and Head Start programs. We need your support now to make sure we’re here as a resource and ready when we can welcome families and students back to our facility. Please consider a gift to the Maryland Science Center. Your support is more important than ever and is greatly appreciated.

